author: gstein
msg: Add a flag that we'll need. mod_dav_svn wants to keep the txn alive,
and will manually commit it. libsvn_repos never keeps a txn alive
beyond the editor drive. This new flag enables the two behaviors.
(make_editor): set the new flag, to be used by complete_cb later.

author: davsclaus
msg: CAMEL-5177: getEndpointUri returns the exact uri the endpoint was given. Avoid reparsing as well. Polished EndpointConfiguration to avoid using PropertyEditorTypeConverter directly.
